      "content": "i've seen all the doctors. they just give me more pills that make me feel like a zombie but the pain is still there. it's not like something that can be 'fixed' anymore. sometimes i just think about how much better it would be if everything was just... still. no more feeling anything at all. wouldn't that just be a mercy compared to this?",
